    "name": "Tommy MC",
    "profile": "Tommy Mc’s blend of unique sounds and distinctive beats creates the perfect blend of dance floor gold that include official remixes of 'Body Talk' (Just Kiddin) which was released on Danny Howard's “ Nothing Else Matters” and later picked up by Sony Music as well as remixes of 'Flowers’ (Feat. Leanne Brown from Sweet Female Attitude) and 'I Need A Miracle' (Guru Project).\r\n\r\nBased at In Demand Music in Liverpool, Tommy also works as a Ghost Producer and Studio Engineer with both his own and client projects going on to be heavily supported on BBC Radio in addition to support from Tiësto, David Guetta, Danny Howard, Sonny Fodera at Creamfields, EDX, The Magician, Futuristic Polar Bears, Judge Jules and Don Diablo.\r\n \r\nIf this wasn’t enough, the music Tommy has been involved in creating has generated over 17.8 million plays, achieved chart success, has been licensed in multiple territories and appeared on such labels as 3Beat, All Around The World, Armada Music, Columbia Records, EDM.com",
